Controller webserver for Tadpoles game located at https://github.com/dileepvr/Tadpole_SDL

Code snippets from:
http://socket.io/get-started/chat/ for basic socket.io configuration
https://gist.github.com/tedmiston/5935757 for node.js net package
http://pages.uoregon.edu/wwe/21.html for html keyboard input


Requirements: Node.js npm socket.io express
sudo apt-get install nodejs
npm install socket.io
npm install express@4.10.2


Usage:
Start tadpoles:   ./tadpoles
Start webserver:   nodejs index.js
Visit localhost:3000 with browser to initiate a tadpole

Use up/down/left/right to control the tadpole or press the arrow buttons on screen.


Files:
index.js serves index.html and opens socket connection to tadpole game to transmit commands.

index.html contains javascript for input and to connect to node.js server with socket.io
